flowchart LR
  WB[Weekly Board] --> ID[Route ID or tick]
  ID --> CARD[Route Card]
  ID --> GOV[Governance Contract]
  CARD --> ACTION[Bounded Action]
  GOV --> QUALITY[Quality Criteria]
  ACTION --> STATE[State Source]
  ACTION --> EVIDENCE[Evidence Source]
  STATE --> NEXT[Next Pointer]
  EVIDENCE --> REVIEW[Weekly Review]

  WB -. Monday Bridge marker .-> BRIDGE[Separate Monday Bridge Sheet]
  BRIDGE --> NEXT
